data.chText: 很多草本植物能在室内种植。
data.enText: Many herbs can be grown indoors.

value.def: If something happens indoors, it happens inside a building.

example.ex: Since she was indoors, she had not been wearing a coat...
example.tran: 由于她在室内,就没有穿外套。

example.ex: I think perhaps we should go indoors...
example.tran: 我觉得也许我们应该进屋里去。

example.ex: Spend an evening indoors watching TV.

trans: 呆在室内；待在室內；待在室内
